LexicalAnalyzer
LexicalAnalyzer is a custom-made scanner to be used in CS3200 Programming Languages.
Lexicon
Lexicon is a Hashtable (String, String) containing the tokens of the language, defined as the key-value [lexeme, token-name] The file lexicon.txt defines the tokens and the lexemes of the language.
